Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Connect AgentRL self-evolution loop to real-world big-corp benchmarks:
NVIDIA SOL-ExecBench, Google DeepSearchQA, Scale AI ToolComp, Princeton HAL.

environment.py (M201-M206):
  EnvironmentConfig: +bench_endpoints (dict), +bench_mode (local/external/hybrid)
  EnvironmentState: +last_bench_response, +bench_call_count
  step() info: +bench_source key
  get_metrics(): +bench_calls, +bench_success_rate

reward.py (M207-M210):
  RewardConfig: +bench_reward_weight, +bench_score_transform
  PolicyReward.__call__: handles bench_result in context (SOL-Score→reward)
  get_stats(): +bench_rewards_total, +bench_calls_count
  create_policy_reward: optional kernel for bench-only mode
  CompositeReward: optional components for empty init

runner.py (M211-M213):
  GovernedRollout: +bench_source, +task_id/agent_id/steps compat aliases
  PolicyViolation: +bench_context, +type alias for violation_type

emitter.py (M214-M216):
  LightningSpan: +bench_source, +bench_score, +agent_id compat
  to_dict(): includes bench fields
  get_stats(): +bench_span_count
  create_emitter(): optional flight_recorder with agent_id fallback

TDD: 94% initial failure (50/53) → 100% pass (53/53) in 1 iteration.
Function counts: environment 12/12, reward 12/12, runner 19/19. Unchanged.
